{
  "name": "Spirit Walker Starter Template (Caminante Espiritual)",
  "author": "poe2-claude",
  "description": "<l>{<gold>{Spirit Walker Starter Template}}\n\n<m>{<silver>{This is a starter template, NOT a finished build.}}\n\n<m>{<red>{IMPORTANT}}: most node and skill IDs in this file are <red>{[Inference]} based on naming patterns. The Spirit Walker ascendancy is brand-new in patch 0.5 and the canonical IDs from repoe-fork/poe2 should be checked before relying on this file.\n\n<m>{<silver>{Plantilla inicial de Caminante Espiritual, no es una build terminada.}}\n\n<m>{<red>{IMPORTANTE}}: muchos IDs en este fichero son <red>{[Inferencias]} basadas en patrones de nomenclatura. La ascendencia Caminante Espiritual es nueva en el parche 0.5; verificar los IDs canónicos en repoe-fork/poe2 antes de usar este fichero en serio.\n\n<grey>{Usage / Uso\n-------------------\n1. Drop into Documents/My Games/Path of Exile 2/BuildPlanner/\n2. Restart the client to ensure the File Watcher picks it up\n3. Open the Passive Tree / Skill Gem panel in-game to see the hints}",
  "ascendancy": "Huntress3",
  "passives": [
    {
      "id": "AscendancyHuntress3Notable1",
      "additional_text": "<m>{<green>{The Natural Order} <silver>{(EN) — grants Tame Beast on Unique Beasts.}}\n<m>{<green>{El Orden Natural} <silver>{(ES) — concede Domar Bestia sobre Bestias Únicas.}}\n\n<grey>{[Inference] node ID. Verify in repoe-fork/poe2.}"
    },
    {
      "id": "AscendancyHuntress3Notable2",
      "additional_text": "<m>{<green>{Wild Protector} <silver>{(EN) — summons a Bear Spirit as a second Companion.}}\n<m>{<green>{Protector Salvaje} <silver>{(ES) — invoca un Espíritu Oso como segundo Compañero.}}\n\n<grey>{[Inference] node ID.}"
    },
    {
      "id": "AscendancyHuntress3Notable3",
      "additional_text": "<m>{<green>{Vivid Stampede} <silver>{(EN) — every 20m moved grants a Vivid Wisp stack; attacking unleashes Stag Spirits.}}\n<m>{<green>{Estampida Vívida} <silver>{(ES) — cada 20m recorridos otorga un cargo de Fuego Fatuo Vívido; atacar libera Espíritus de Ciervo.}}\n\n<grey>{[Inference] node ID.}"
    },
    {
      "id": "AscendancyHuntress3Notable4",
      "additional_text": "<m>{<green>{Primal Bounty} <silver>{(EN) — Empowered Projectile Skills fire more projectiles with increased Projectile Speed.}}\n<m>{<green>{Generosidad Primigenia} <silver>{(ES) — las habilidades de proyectil empoderadas disparan más proyectiles a mayor velocidad.}}\n\n<grey>{[Inference] node ID.}"
    },
    {
      "id": "AscendancyHuntress3Notable5",
      "additional_text": "<m>{<gold>{Sacred Unity} <silver>{(EN) — bonus capstone, free to allocate if Wild Protector + Vivid Stampede + Primal Bounty are all taken.}}\n<m>{<gold>{Unidad Sagrada} <silver>{(ES) — capstone bono, gratuito si Protector Salvaje + Estampida Vívida + Generosidad Primigenia están asignados.}}\n\n<grey>{[Inference] node ID.}"
    }
  ],
  "skills": [
    {
      "id": "Metadata/Items/Gems/SkillGemVividStampede",
      "additional_text": "<m>{<green>{Core mobility + damage skill}} (EN)\n<m>{<green>{Habilidad principal de movilidad y daño}} (ES)\n\n<grey>{[Inference] gem metadata path. The Vivid Stampede skill is new in 0.5 — confirm the exact Metadata/Items/Gems/... path with poe2_db_lookup or by inspecting a PoB2 export of a real Spirit Walker build.}",
      "support_skills": []
